{"article_id":"BdhXPi1Tr13R3qRt","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump said Friday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"he could declare a national emergency on the border","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"and order his government to build fencing","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"without needing to go to Congress for additional funding .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"\" I can do it","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"if I want , \"","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"he said ,","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"adding ,","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"\" I may do it . \"","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"He said","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"he ' s still interested in trying to get a deal done with Congress","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"on funding his border wall plans ,","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"but he made clear","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"he hasn ' t foreclosed other options","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"for erecting the barrier","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"he promised voters in 2016","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"would be built","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"and paid for by Mexico .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Mr. Trump last month had raised the prospect","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"of declaring an emergency","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"and asking the Defense Department to construct barriers outside of the normal congressional appropriations process .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"The Pentagon at the time said","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"it had not developed those plans ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"but said","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"it did have legal authority","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"to build a wall","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"if it were deemed part of a counter-drug operation or part of a national emergency .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"The president for months has said","depth":4},{"id":28,"text":"the country is facing such an emergency .","depth":4},{"id":29,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s comments Friday came after a meeting with congressional leaders on strategies","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"to end the partial government shutdown ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"which began two weeks ago","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"after Mr. Trump said","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"he wouldn ' t accept any spending bills","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"unless he was given wall money .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"That was a reversal for the president ,","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"who just days before had signaled through his staff","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that he would sign the bills","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"and he would try to find money elsewhere","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"to make good on his campaign wall promise .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Congressional Democrats said","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"Mr. Trump would be abusing his powers","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"if he were to declare what one called \" a phony national emergency . \"","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"\" Defense spending is for national defense , not the Trump campaign ' s political wish list , \"","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"said Sen. Jack Reed , the top Democrat on the Senate Armed Services Committee .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"And Rep. Adam Smith , incoming Democratic chairman of the House Armed Services Committee , said","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"the president would be shortchanging the military","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"if he asked it to use its manpower and money","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"to build fencing .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Mr. Reed vowed to rally bipartisan opposition to Mr. Trump","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"should the president pursue the emergency strategy .","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"Mr. Reed said","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"Mr. Trump had a GOP Congress for two years","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"and didn ' t get his wall funding ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"but \" now , suddenly , he wants the Pentagon to foot the bill . \"","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Mr. Trump did actually win more than $ 1 billion in money","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"to build levee wall and border fencing in the 2018 spending bills ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"and construction of the 100 or so miles","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"covered by that money","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"is ongoing .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"But that bill prohibited the administration from using any updated wall designs , such as the concrete models","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"the president had Homeland Security test in San Diego .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Border Patrol agents said","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"they weren ' t interested in the test designs anyway ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"they prefer the steel bollard fencing","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"that ' s become standard since passage of the Secure Fence Act of 2006 .","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"Mr. Smith voted for that 2006 bill ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"which mandated 700 miles of two-tier fencing .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Mr. Reed voted against that bill .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":139,"left":87,"right":138,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":78,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":73,"right":77,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":0,"right":72,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":72,"left":1,"right":71,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":75,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":86,"left":80,"right":85,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":80,"left":9,"right":79,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":79,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"